data.description: Welcome to this nicely updated 1920 square foot home. The house features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms as well as newer appliances, updated flooring, and an extensive solar system. This property sits outside of the city limits of Central Point and boasts over .65 acres of flat useable land. The home sits off the road and has a country feeling. There is also plenty of room for your trailers/RV's and the toys that go with them. This is a must see!
